title: F-66 - Give It A Try (Single 1980)
description:
F-66 - Give It A Try (Single 1980)

RAPP RECORDS


Line Up:

Ray Gillen - Lead Vocals
Gary Garrammone - Guitar
Brian Chris - Bass
Frankie Attitude - Drums and Backing Vocals on "It Doesn't Matter"

Both songs are written by Gary Garrammone.

It is ripped straight from my original single 7'' on 320 kbps mp3 format.

This is the first recording ever from Ray Gillen and this torrent
is dedicated to his memory for the 21st anniversary of his death (01/12/1993).

It is also dedicated to the memory of the rest fallen members of this band
(Gary and Brian) and the only surviving member, Frankie.
